      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Still Remember</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Still remember, cannot forget the flower in your hair. </l>
          <l>Looking forward listen to my heart </l>
          <l>Listen and shed a tear </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>Chorus: </l>
          <l>Waiting for you long time baby was so hard for me to do, </l>
          <l>Me and you forever we'll be one but now you're gone </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>And I, still remember cannot forget the brightness of your smile </l>
          <l>Soft embraces the look into your eyes </l>
          <l>The whisper in my ear </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>Chorus: </l>
          <l>Waiting for you..</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
